node.text:
Day ✌🏼 in the olympic village 
Preparation is going well and the food is delicioussss 😋 
So many new impressions here and I‘m so greatful to be part of @teamdeutschland 🙏🏼☺️
📸 @huettehuette 
#anzeige #olympics #olympics2020 #trackandfield

node.text:
Last night in Germany ❤️ tomorrow I‘m off to Japan 🇯🇵🥰 
#trackandfield #running #passion #lovewhatyoudo #workhard #tokyo2020

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by ᗩlica Ѕchmidt on July 14, 2021 tagging @foodspring. May be an image of 1 person, standing, outdoors and text that says 'foodspring'.

node.text:
Anzeige/ Last tough session before heading to Tokyo is in the books🙏🏼 Hardly survived it😅 
Wie immer dürfen bei mir vor wichtigen Einheiten die Energy aminos von @foodspring nicht fehlen um den Fokus zu finden 🙏🏼 mit meinem Code: alicaFSG 15% sparen.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ᗩlica Ѕchmidt on July 12, 2021. May be an image of 1 person.
Photo by ᗩlica Ѕchmidt on July 08, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text: The last session before my next competition is done. On Saturday I run the 400m again, that is the last competition before I go to Tokyo 💓🥰 #trackandfield #running #lovewhatyoudo #4x4 #tokyo2020 #passion

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by ᗩlica Ѕchmidt on July 03, 2021 tagging @alicasmd. May be an image of 1 person and stadium.

node.text:
TOKYO IS CALLING - I‘m going to the Olympics!🥺🇯🇵

Still feels unreal! I’m so grateful and at the same time thrilled to experience something I have been dreaming of since I started all of this! Bring it on - I so can’t wait for this 🙆🏼‍♀️😍
_________
#trackandfield#olympia#olympics#roadtotokyo#running#runningmotivation#dreamcomestrue#run#sportmotivation#tokyo2020

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by ᗩlica Ѕchmidt on July 01, 2021 tagging @pumarunning. May be an image of one or more people and people playing sports.

node.text:
Passion ⚡️

Anzeige/ Beat your time then beat it again in Deviate NITRO. ⏰💥 #RUNPuma
Was ich am meisten da diesem Schuh liebe ist, dass er super leicht ist und durch die Carbon Sohle super federt 🙏🏼

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by ᗩlica Ѕchmidt on June 30, 2021 tagging @alicasmd, and @foodspring. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'PROTEIN'.

node.text:
Anzeige/ Be thankful for where you are now and keep fighting and working hard for what you want tomorrow 🙏🏼
Was bei mir nach oder teilweise auch während einem workout nie fehlen darf ist ein Snack 😋🙌🏼 entweder ein Proteinriegel oder ein Whey Shake um meine Muskeln optimal zu versorgen ☺️ 
Mit meinem Code alicaFSG spart ihr wie immer 15 auf alles 🙈 
#trackandfield #running #trainhard #recoversmart  #foodspringfamily #foodspringcode
